# 0-work workspace

`0-work/` is the agent context space for this project. Application code lives outside it.

## Layout

- `0-work/docs/spec.md` — project objectives and agent brief. **Read before planning or executing.**
- `0-work/plans/` — execution plans. One file per major effort; do not scatter plans in the repo root.
- `0-work/scripts/` — side effects (API calls, deploys, git push). Log every run in `0-work/scripts/log.md`.
- `0-work/scripts/.env` — credentials (gitignored). Never commit or echo secrets.

## Script log

After running any script under `0-work/scripts/`, append to `log.md`:

```markdown
## YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM — script-name
- **Command:** `...`
- **Exit:** 0
- **Result:** ...
```

## Agent brief updates

When project state changes materially, update the **Agent brief** section in `spec.md` (current state, next action, open decisions).
